_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473550/extras/95c1b8090fdd978a88386737ba87e189.poster.avif?t=1742962722\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473550/extras/95c1b8090fdd978a88386737ba87e189.webm?t=1742962722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473550/extras/3e0f32a75ddd5195ff4af88d592fc88e.poster.avif?t=1742962722\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473550/extras/3e0f32a75ddd5195ff4af88d592fc88e.webm?t=1742962722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
